data.description: Opportunity knocks! New Kitchen updates, with this 5 bedroom 2 bath that offers space that can be reimagined for your personal needs! Tucked in this well established community with NO HOA, this home is conveniently located close to main highways for commutes to Tampa, Riverview, or other central Florida attractions. Eateries and shopping close by.  Split floor plan offers privacy in three ways.  Serene water views from the back yard add to the enchantment of early morning coffee or sunset views at the end of the day.  The back yard fenced for pet security. Storage options are plentiful, and a new roof will be installed prior to closing!
